<TEXT>
<P>
SHANGHAI, October 16 (Xinhua) -- Veteran strongwoman Wei
Xiangyin claimed her 83-kg category weightlifting title with world
records at the Eighth National Games here Thursday evening.
</P>
<P>
Wei lifted 137.5 kgs in snatch and 155 kgs in jerk for a
two-lift total of 292.5 kgs, all surpassing the listed world
marks.
</P>
