shopping centers, and scientific research institutes that
belonged to the Dongfang (Orient) International Group's Shanghai
Municipal Silk Imports and Exports Company and the Shanghai
Textile Holdings Corp.'s Shanghai Jinda International Silk Co. Ltd.
</P>
