Corporation (UPTC) have been divided into two bodies as from
yesterday, "The Monitor" reported today.
</P>
<P>
Uganda Telecom Ltd (UTL) and Uganda Post Ltd (UPL) will be
coordinated by UPTC headquarters under the board of directors
until they are registered as private limited companies, the
report said.
</P>
<P>
