said.
</P>
<P>
UPTC board of directors nominated three committees to preside
over the division.
</P>
<P>
Richard Owora, principal public relation officer of UPTC, said
the workers of UPTC are regrouping, and the separate budgets are
being prepared now for a smooth transition.
</P>
<P>
The division will not effect the normal works of the two new
bodies, the officer promised.
</P>
<P>
The preparing works for the division started in April this
year. 
