<HEADLINE> Weather Forecast for Major Chinese Cities </HEADLINE>
<TEXT>
<P>
BEIJING, October 16 (Xinhua) -- Weather forecast for 14 major
Chinese cities for the next 24 hours from 20:00 today to 20:00 on
October 17 issued by China's Central Meteorological Station at
17:00 today:
</P>
<P>
Beijing: min. 10 degrees C., max. 22 degrees C., cloudy to
clear, calm to fresh breeze.
</P>
<P>
Shenyang: min. 3 degrees C., max. 13 degrees C., clear to
cloudy, calm to gentle breeze.
</P>
<P>
Tianjin: min. 10 degrees C., max. 21 degrees C., clear, calm to
gentle breeze.
</P>
<P>
Xi'an: min. 10 degrees C., max. 23 degrees C., clear, calm to
gentle breeze.
