<TEXT>
<P>
JERUSALEM, October 16 (Xinhua) -- Israeli police have detained
10 Jewish residents in Jerusalem for illegally selling explosives
to Palestinians, including Islamic militants, Israel Radio
reported today.
</P>
<P>
The arrested are authorized workers to carry out detonation
works in quarries inside Israel, but they also worked in quarries
within the Palestinian territories.
