and falling revenues mean that the sale of state enterprises will
be the main source of cash for the country, he said.
</P>
<P>
In order to speed up privatization, Thaksin said, the
government would soon issue a corporatization act which covers
guidelines of privatization processes.
</P>
<P>
He said that over the next one to two years, state enterprises
will be required to implement conduct-clear plans for
privatization. 
