<HEADLINE> Earthquake Hits Southwestern Part of Xinjiang </HEADLINE>
<TEXT>
<P>
BEIJING, October 15 (Xinhua) -- An earthquake measuring 5.1 on
Richter scale jolted the Kunlun Mountian in the southwestern tip
of China's Xinjiang Uygur Autonomous Region, northwest China, at
04:30 hours (Beijing time) today.
