<HEADLINE> Czech Republic Increases Beer Export </HEADLINE>
<TEXT>
<P>
PRAGUE, October 15 (Xinhua) -- The Czech Republic's beer
exports totalled 150 million liters during the first half of this
year, up 12.5 percent over the same period of last year. the Beer
Association said today.
</P>
<P>
