third for Mitsubishi, has 56 points, nine more than Spain's Carlos
Sainz who was fourth for Ford.
</P>
<P>
McRae is third with 42 points with two rounds of this year's
14-round series remaining.
</P>
<P>
Makinen, Sainz and McRae are now the only competitors for this
year's title. The last two rallies are in Australia and Britain.
